{"type":"text","timestamp":1775889647112,"sessionID":"ses_284bc2356ffen9PxcrKpTk3VSR","part":{"id":"prt_d7b454933001u4BHjO8PIQJ3Ih","messageID":"msg_d7b4530d5001Yxgz73CK6DwsKF","sessionID":"ses_284bc2356ffen9PxcrKpTk3VSR","type":"text","text":"## Verification Report: Dify Plugin Integration (AR-036)\n\n### ✅ PASS: File Structure\nAll required files present and correctly organized:\n- ✅ `main.py` \n- ✅ `manifest.yaml`\n- ✅ `provider/agentcube.yaml`\n- ✅ `provider/agentcube.py`\n- ✅ `tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml`\n- ✅ `tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py`\n- ✅ `requirements.txt`\n- ✅ Documentation files (GUIDE.md, README.md, PRIVACY.md, .difyignore)\n- ✅ Icon files (icon.png, icon-dark.png)\n\n### ✅ PASS: main.py\n`main.py:4` - Correctly implements `Plugin(DifyPluginEnv(MAX_REQUEST_TIMEOUT=120)).run()`\n\n### ✅ PASS: manifest.yaml\nAll required keys and values match spec exactly:\n- ✅ version: \"0.0.2\", type: plugin, author: volcano-sh, name: agentcube\n- ✅ Multilingual labels (en_US, ja_JP, zh_Hans, pt_BR)\n- ✅ icon/icon_dark fields present\n- ✅ resource subtree with memory and permission flags\n- ✅ meta.version/arch/runner/minimum_dify_version\n- ✅ created_at, privacy, repo, verified fields\n\n### ✅ PASS: provider/agentcube.yaml\nStructure matches spec:\n- ✅ identity with multilingual fields\n- ✅ Commented-out oauth_schema block\n- ✅ tools list\n- ✅ extra.python.source\n\n### ✅ PASS: provider/agentcube.py\n`provider/agentcube.py:6-19` - Implements `AgentcubeCodeInterpreterProvider` with `_validate_credentials` method matching spec pattern\n\n### ❌ FAIL: tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml\n**CRITICAL DEVIATION FROM SPEC:**\n\n**Expected per spec (`integrations/design.md:51-52`):**\n```yaml\n- name: router_url\n  form: form  # Configuration field\n- name: workload_manager_url\n  form: form  # Configuration field\n```\n\n**Actual (`tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml:28,42`):**\n```yaml\n- name: router_url\n  form: llm  # WRONG - should be \"form\"\n- name: workload_manager_url\n  form: llm  # WRONG - should be \"form\"\n```\n\n**Impact:** `form: llm` means these credentials must be provided by the LLM on every invocation, when they should be configured once in the provider settings (`form: form`).\n\n### ✅ PASS: tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml (other fields)\n- ✅ All 8 parameters present with correct names/types/required flags\n- ✅ language options: python, javascript, typescript\n- ✅ All labels and descriptions (human/llm) present\n- ✅ extra.python.source correct\n\n### ⚠️ PARTIAL: tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py\n`tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py:9-87` - Core implementation correct:\n- ✅ `AgentcubeCodeInterpreterTool` class\n- ✅ `_invoke` method yields ToolInvokeMessage\n- ✅ `execute` method with all parameters\n- ✅ Code and command execution logic\n- ✅ Error handling (CommandExecutionError, general exceptions)\n\n**Minor deviation:** Uses `Optional[str]` type hints which are more explicit than spec but semantically equivalent.\n\n### ✅ PASS: requirements.txt\n`requirements.txt:1-2` - Contains:\n```\ndify-plugin>=0.4.2,<0.5.0\nagentcube-sdk>=0.0.10\n```\n\nNote: `dify-plugin==0.0.1b22` is only available version in environment, but spec constraint is correct.\n\n### ✅ PASS: Test Coverage\n- ✅ `test_provider.py` - 15 tests for provider validation\n- ✅ `test_tool.py` - 19 tests for tool execution\n- ✅ `test_integration.py` - 14 tests for full workflow\n\nTests cannot run due to environment (Python 3.9 vs dify-plugin 3.10+ requirement), but test structure and coverage are comprehensive.\n\n---\n\n### Summary\n\n| Component | Status | Notes |\n|-----------|--------|-------|\n| File structure | ✅ PASS | All files present |\n| main.py | ✅ PASS | Matches spec |\n| manifest.yaml | ✅ PASS | Matches spec exactly |\n| provider/agentcube.yaml | ✅ PASS | Matches spec |\n| provider/agentcube.py | ✅ PASS | Matches spec |\n| tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml | ❌ **FAIL** | router_url/workload_manager_url form field wrong |\n| tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py | ✅ PASS | Matches spec (minor type hint difference) |\n| requirements.txt | ✅ PASS | Matches spec |\n| Tests | ✅ PASS | Comprehensive coverage |\n\n**Result: FAIL** - Critical deviation in tool parameter form fields requires correction.","time":{"start":1775889647109,"end":1775889647109}}}
